v1.0.0 [May 1, 2026]
- migrated to Manifest V3
- fixed numbers not recognized as first array element
- added support for exponent notation in numbers
- reject invalid leading zeros in numbers
- fixed HTML closing tag order in formatted output
- fixed escaped JSON not recursively unescaped
- added undo (Alt+Z) to revert last format
- fixed crash when array contains null in escaped JSON mode
- capped undo history to prevent memory leaks
- added strict mode
- fixed repeated formatting nesting pre/code tags
- fixed multiple JSONs in one node only formatting the first one

v0.1.3 [Dec 29, 2018]
- fixed html escape bug

v0.1.2 [Dec 26, 2018]
- improve json extraction performance

v0.1.1 [Dec 25, 2018]
- fixed leading whitespace causing payload not being recognized

v0.1.0 [Dec 25, 2018]
- extract json instead of guessing {},[]
- using innerHTML instead of adding DOM
- flash feedback when cannot parse

v0.0.1 [Dec 12, 2018]
- working POC